description.p:
the temperature of the exhaust gases and residues is kept below a threshold to prevent destruction of the trapping agents;


the temperature of the exhaust gases and residues is kept within a predetermined temperature range corresponding to the optimal operating range of the trap means;


heating of the passenger compartment of the vehicle is improved, in particular the speed at which the environment parameters converge is increased, by heating the fluid feeding the heating radiator of the heating and/or air conditioning installation;


a back-pressure is generated at the exhaust to accelerate warming up of the engine if the access control means shut off the communicating passage.
